784
00:58:43,983 --> 00:58:46,781
I'm breaking all the rules now anyway.

785
00:58:46,781 --> 00:58:48,979
Since I'm going to hell.

786
00:58:53,392 --> 00:58:56,190
So, does a person have to be dying

787
00:58:58,764 --> 00:59:00,664
to become like you?

