793
00:59:22,721 --> 00:59:23,881
<i>What was it like?</i>

794
00:59:25,057 --> 00:59:27,423
<i>The venom was excruciating.</i>

795
00:59:28,127 --> 00:59:30,288
<i>But what Carlisle did was much harder.</i>

796
00:59:30,288 --> 00:59:32,830
