01:14:07,672 --> 01:14:08,933
What?

976
01:14:10,709 --> 01:14:12,506
Forks is growing on me.

977
01:14:12,506 --> 01:14:15,444
Could a guy have anything to do with that?

978
01:14:15,444 --> 01:14:17,640
Well, yeah.

