with my family.

1018
01:18:25,393 --> 01:18:26,452
Baseball?

1019
01:18:26,452 --> 01:18:28,431
Yes, sir, that's the plan.

1020
01:18:28,431 --> 01:18:30,694
Bella's gonna play baseball.

1021
01:18:31,836 --> 01:18:33,531
Well, good luck with that.

1022
01:18:33,531 --> 01:18:36,402
