1023
01:18:39,444 --> 01:18:40,775
Hey.

1024
01:18:41,779 --> 01:18:43,713
Still got that pepper spray?

1025
01:18:43,713 --> 01:18:45,214
Yeah, Dad.

1026
01:18:50,455 --> 01:18:53,185
And since when do vampires like baseball?

1027
01:18:53,185 --> 01:18:55,987
Well, it's the American pastime,

1028
01:18:55,987 --> 01:18:58,620
and there's a thunderstorm coming.

1029
